<!-- REST API Test Suite for Live Monitoring -->

@hostname = localhost
@port = 7071
@baseUrl = http://{{hostname}}:{{port}}/api

### 🏥 Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Accept: application/json

### 🤖 List All Bots
GET {{baseUrl}}/bot-api
Accept: application/json

### 🤖 Create New Bot (Price Alert)
POST {{baseUrl}}/bot-api
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bitcoin Price Alert",
  "strategy": "price-alert",
  "coins": ["bitcoin", "ethereum", "cardano"],
  "enabled": true,
  "params": {
    "priceAlert": {
      "alerts": [
        {
          "coin": "bitcoin",
          "targetPrice": 95000,
          "direction": "above"
        },
        {
          "coin": "ethereum",
          "targetPrice": 3500,
          "direction": "below"
        }
      ]
    }
  }
}

### 🤖 Create Opportunity Detector Bot
POST {{baseUrl}}/bot-api
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Opportunity Detector",
  "strategy": "opportunity-detector",
  "coins": ["solana", "polkadot", "avalanche"],
  "enabled": true,
  "params": {
    "opportunityDetector": {
      "minChangePercent": 5,
      "volumeMultiplier": 2,
      "timeframeHours": 24
    }
  }
}

### 📊 Crypto Prices (CoinGecko)
GET {{baseUrl}}/crypto?ids=bitcoin,ethereum,cardano,solana

### 💰 Crypto Premium (with advanced metrics)
GET {{baseUrl}}/crypto-premium?ids=bitcoin,ethereum&metrics=market_data,market_cap,volume

### 🪵 Get Blob Storage Info
GET {{baseUrl}}/blob

### 📋 Health Status Verbose
GET {{baseUrl}}/health?verbose=true

###
# Testing Notes:
# 1. Run Frontend: pnpm -C apps/web dev (port 3000)
# 2. Run API: pnpm -C api start (port 7071)
# 3. Use these requests with "Send Request" button
# 4. Check terminal output for logs
# 5. Monitor response times and status codes
#
# Keyboard Shortcut: Ctrl+Alt+R to send request
# Or click "Send Request" link above each request
###
